summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2768 for the improvement of First Avenue South, from Hanford Street to Dawson Street, all in the City of Seattle, by replanking the deck of the existing trestle, under Ordinance No. 33082, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
